Enum Nutrient

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Nutrient>
cmu.edu.andrew.spoonacular.Nutrient
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Nutrient>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Nutrient
extends java.lang.Enum<Nutrient>
An enum representing a nutrient. Can be used to calculate the percent daily value of an amount of the nutrient.
